    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《墨笔斗妖传 Inkbrush: The Demon Wars》是一款2D回合制策略类游戏，玩家将执掌一支由水墨毛笔少年与他的伙伴组成的队伍，在山海绘卷式大地图中探索前行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗中可采集材料，打造装备与道具，强化角色实力，解锁多样技能树与成长路线。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔ <strong>战棋策略 × 地形互动</strong><br>利用环境要素打出特殊伤害。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/410a31d6fbb5a31dc3825eb2a677fb23.poster.avif?t=1752829778\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/410a31d6fbb5a31dc3825eb2a677fb23.webm?t=1752829778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/410a31d6fbb5a31dc3825eb2a677fb23.mp4?t=1752829778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>技能树与队伍构建</strong><br>解锁多样技能，自由养成角色，搭配出独一无二的战斗风格与小队组合。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/8eebd1e43b6a4c7811b4deb4da681cbe.poster.avif?t=1752829778\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/8eebd1e43b6a4c7811b4deb4da681cbe.webm?t=1752829778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/8eebd1e43b6a4c7811b4deb4da681cbe.mp4?t=1752829778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠 <strong>战斗中采集 × 道具打造</strong><br>在战斗中收集材料，战后打造强化道具，为下次挑战做好准备。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/a849e776f135c305f9db73ec8658e418.poster.avif?t=1752829778\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/a849e776f135c305f9db73ec8658e418.webm?t=1752829778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/a849e776f135c305f9db73ec8658e418.mp4?t=1752829778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐉 <strong>高强度 Boss 战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对血量更高、技能复杂的强大Boss，挑战你的布局与应变极限，感受步步紧逼的压迫感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺 <strong>线性推进的大地图探索</strong><br>如同山水长卷般的大地图中前行，触发战斗、事件与收集点，探索大地图。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/a97bd1355539d5ed2880d7d5bbff5389.poster.avif?t=1752829778\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/a97bd1355539d5ed2880d7d5bbff5389.webm?t=1752829778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597600/extras/a97bd1355539d5ed2880d7d5bbff5389.mp4?t=1752829778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>国风卡通美术 × 古琴笛韵音乐</strong><br>水墨灵感结合卡通表现，搭配古琴与笛子的民族音乐，打造独特的东方幻想氛围。</p></li></ul>",
